{"id":28894,"date":"2024-02-09T21:44:08","date_gmt":"2021-12-09T16:14:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=28894"},"modified":"2022-08-30T15:10:52","modified_gmt":"2022-08-30T09:40:52","slug":"wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinet\/","title":{"rendered":"Top 6 Wall Mounted Bathroom Cabinet Ideas For A Clutter-Free Shower Space"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Make some extra storage space in your washroom with these smart wall mounted bathroom cabinet ideas<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-cabinet-designs\/\">Bathroom cabinets<\/a> are a must for keeping the space neat and clutter-free. As apartments get more compact with time, a spacious bathroom can sometimes be a dream. So if you are living in a petit apartment with a compact washroom, a wall mounted bathroom cabinet is a must for you. Here we bring to you some innovative, space-saving bathroom storage solutions that will help keep your toiletries and other essentials in a clutter-free manner without taking up your floor space. These are incredibly functional and can take your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bathroom-design\/\">bathroom interiors<\/a> to an all-new level. So what are you waiting for? Get ready to explore some smartly designed wall mounted bathroom cabinets that can become the showstopper of your bathroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. A Wall Mounted Bathroom Cabinet In Wood For An Elegant Look<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This bathroom is designed with marble and slate tiles to create a striking contrast and make the space look vibrant. The black wall mounted bathroom cabinet matches seamlessly with the interiors and provides ample storage space. Use the space to store your cleaning essentials and toiletries. We have also added an LED-lit shelf to keep your soap dispenser, perfume diffusers and candles if you please. Be mindful of adding a glass partition to keep the shower area separate. This will help to keep your bathroom clean and dry.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213104\/bathroom-storage-cabinet-wall-mount-in-wood.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom storage cabinets wall mount in the wooden finish with an LED-lit shelf that lends an elegant look\" class=\"wp-image-28897\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213104\/bathroom-storage-cabinet-wall-mount-in-wood.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213104\/bathroom-storage-cabinet-wall-mount-in-wood-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213104\/bathroom-storage-cabinet-wall-mount-in-wood-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213104\/bathroom-storage-cabinet-wall-mount-in-wood-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A black wall mounted bathroom cabinet that blends perfectly with the slate wall tiles<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. White Wall Mounted Bathroom Cabinet To Create A Striking Contrast<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The focal point of this bold and stylish bathroom is the elaborate vanity area. It comes with cabinets, drawers and overhead loft storage. The pull-out unit makes use of the corner space against the wall beautifully. The mirror with backlight illuminates the space and accentuates the beauty of this white wall mounted bathroom cabinet. The white colour cuts the monotony of slate tiles and creates a striking contrast. The multiple storage options elevate the functionality of the bathroom and make it a zero clutter zone.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213130\/white-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinet.jpg\" alt=\"White wall-mounted bathroom cabinet in minimal design with mirror with backlight illuminates the space\" class=\"wp-image-28901\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213130\/white-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinet.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213130\/white-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinet-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213130\/white-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinet-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213130\/white-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinet-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A white wall mounted bathroom cabinet with multiple storage options<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"https:\/\/api.whatsapp.com\/send?phone=916366910437&text=Hello%20Design%20Cafe%20Team,%20I%20am%20interested%20to%20know%20more%20about%20your%20home%20interior%20design%20services\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a dream home with interiors that last a lifetime\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/26185038\/dream-home-with-interiors-that-last-a-lifetime.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Wall Mounted Bathroom Sink Cabinet For A Clean And Clutter-Free Look<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a compact bathroom with not much space for a large cabinet, this vanity unit is perfect for you. The handleless drawers in teal lend a clean look to the area and match the colour scheme. You can also add a tall corner cabinet with sliding doors, as shown in the image, for some additional storage space. The space beneath is intelligently used to house your washing machine. This makes the bathroom multi-functional despite being compact. The teal and white combination makes the bathroom look spacious and adds a fun element to it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213123\/wall-mounted-bathroom-sink-cabinet.jpg\" alt=\"A wall-mounted bathroom sink cabinet with handleless drawers in teal lend a clean look to the area\" class=\"wp-image-28900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213123\/wall-mounted-bathroom-sink-cabinet.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213123\/wall-mounted-bathroom-sink-cabinet-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213123\/wall-mounted-bathroom-sink-cabinet-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213123\/wall-mounted-bathroom-sink-cabinet-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A bathroom designed in white and teal accents with multiple cabinets and a laundry area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Tall Wall Mounted Bathroom Cabinets To Amp Up The Glam Quotient<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This chic bathroom is perfect for people who want to add a luxurious touch to their shower time. The golden fittings lend an elegant look, while the backlit mirror illuminates the space beautifully. We have added a sleek tall wall mounted bathroom cabinet and a vanity unit with drawers to arrange your toiletries and towels in a clutter-free manner. The patterned tiles in pink and white add to the aesthetics of the space. This bathroom oozes a luxurious vibe and can elevate your shower experience by several notches.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213111\/tall-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinets.jpg\" alt=\"A tall wall mounted corner bathroom cabinet and a vanity unit with drawers brings a clutter-free look\" class=\"wp-image-28898\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213111\/tall-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinets.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213111\/tall-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinets-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213111\/tall-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinets-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213111\/tall-wall-mounted-bathroom-cabinets-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A plush bathroom interior design with a tall wall mounted bathroom cabinet and golden fittings<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Bathroom Storage Cabinets Wall Mount With Mirror That Are Perfect For Small Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This wall-mounted cabinet is hidden behind the mirror and thus doesn&#8217;t take up any extra space on the floor or walls. The design is fuss-free and perfectly suits bathrooms of any size. The huge mirror reflects light beautifully and creates an illusion of a bigger space. We have also added wall sconces on either side to highlight the vanity unit.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213058\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-with-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom storage cabinets wall mount with mirror design is fuss-free and perfectly suits bathrooms of any size\" class=\"wp-image-28896\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213058\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-with-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213058\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-with-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213058\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-with-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213058\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-with-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A wall mounted bathroom cabinet with a mirror to amp up your shower area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. A Wall Mounted Bathroom Cabinet With An Open Shelf To Display Knick-Knacks<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This tall wall mounted bathroom cabinet designed in wooden laminate matches seamlessly with the bathroom&#8217;s yellow and white colour scheme. The open shelf in between helps to arrange your soap dispensers and shampoo bottles in an accessible range. The floating vanity unit with matching laminates adds extra storage space, while the floral patterned wall tiles add a fun element to the entire design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213051\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-india-with-an-open-shelf.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom storage cabinets wall mount India designed in wooden laminate with an open shelf to display knick-knack\" class=\"wp-image-28895\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213051\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-india-with-an-open-shelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213051\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-india-with-an-open-shelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213051\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-india-with-an-open-shelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/09213051\/bathroom-storage-cabinets-wall-mount-india-with-an-open-shelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\"